</P>
<P>
	Neighbors said they heard the father of Joseph Lewis Martinez  
screaming shortly before sheriff's deputies arrived at the house 
early Thursday. Lanexa is a rural community in New Kent County, 
about 35 miles east of Richmond. 
</P>
