</P>
<P>
	``Fox News Sunday'' -- Topics: Buchanan-Reform Party,  
investigating Justice, TV smut. Guests: GOP presidential candidate 
Pat Buchanan, Sen. Arlen Specter, R-Pa., ``Touched by an Angel'' 
executive producer Martha Williamson. 
  	   	
